<s>hi.</s><s> i've searched the forums and had a chat with live support; it doesn't appear as if business catalyst has done anything about the eu cookie law which will become enforcable from 26th may 2012. 
</s><s>the law came into existence on 26th may 2011, but because of its potentially severe consequences and horrified reaction from the internet community, the ico added 1 years grace period for businesses to become compliant. 
