<post author="EZ-BC-Team" timestamp="Jun 9, 2013 11:40 PM">
<s>hello simon and everyone ! 
</s><s>we did an overview of eu cookie law requirements for various european countries in our blog.</s><s> in two words, basically there are as many cookie laws as there are countries in the eu, since every country has their own requirements.if you are based in sweden and you're building a website that will operate in france then you have to comply with the french legal framework. 
</s><s>in the uk, for example, implied consent is sufficient.</s><s> legislation of portugal requires you to receive an explicit consent via pop-up, banner or lightbox.</s><s> in netherlands, cookies can only be stored or read if you have obtained the visitor's consent.</s><s> this consent must be obtained prior to storing or reading the cookies.</s><s> there's an ios app called cookielaw that can help you identify the requirements for your site. 
</s></post>
</TEXT>
